overview: Samantha ‘Sam’ Abrams is a witty, studious, and street-smart high school senior from New York City, adjusting to a new reality after her family relocates to a rural southern community in Tennessee. Once the culture-shock wears off,  she stumbles into feelings for a charming, yet wayward boy named Dillon, a country boy, high school athlete with a maverick’s spirit.  With Sam adamantly focused on her future, and Dillon contently stuck in idle, the two learn that sometimes the most unsuspecting people in life have the most meaningful impact.
title: Something Here
